### Project Description
[ReverseMind Calc 🌀
A playful twist on ordinary calculators — in ReverseMind Calc, the buttons lie! Press “+” and you’ll subtract, hit “-” and you’ll divide. With colorful buttons, emoji feedback, and random background colors, it turns simple math into a fun brain-bending challenge.
]

### The Problem (that doesn't exist)
Traditional calculators are boring and predictable. Students and math lovers lose focus quickly, and people rarely challenge their mental agility once they master basic operations. There’s no fun in pressing “+” and always getting addition — where’s the excitement?

### The Solution (that nobody asked for)
ReverseMind Calc turns arithmetic into a surprise-filled challenge by flipping the meaning of operations. Press “+” to subtract, “-” to divide, “*” to add, and “/” to multiply. Combined with vibrant colors, emojis, and random backgrounds, it transforms mundane calculations into a playful mental workout, keeping users engaged and laughing while sharpening their thinking skills.

